    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Juliann D, I haven&#39;t tried using a broiler for this, so I can&#39;t say for certain, but I think it could work.  You&#39;ll need to watch it closely, because it&#39;ll brown a lot faster than it does with the torch, but go for it.</p>
    </div>

